Version: 1.0.0 RC1

LogRhythm.Tools is a PowerShell module for interacting with LogRhythm APIs.


LogRhythm Components:

  • Admin
  • AIE Drilldown
  • Cases
  • Echo
  • Search

Third Party Integrations:

  • Virus Total
  • Recorded Future
  • Shodan
  • Urlscan


Authors: Gene Cupstid & Eric Hart

https://github.com/LogRhythm-Tools/LogRhythm.Tools




Last Update: 6/26/2020

Permissions

Ability to download resources from Github.com
Ability to extract archive files from zip
User level privileges to run PowerShell
User level privileges to install PowerShell modules

Required Credentials

LogRhythm API Key

Optional Credentials

Recorded future API Key
Shodan API Key
Urlscan API Key
VirusTotal API Key
